💥2x Technical Business Analyst, Contract
💷 £575 per day Inside IR35
📍London based, 1 day per week in the office

We're working with one of the biggest names in British Media and Publishing. They're looking for a 2x talented Technical Business Analyst's to join their team and have a strong focus on understanding the impact of changes across a few of their brands. 

You'll lead close collaboration with Engineering on the architecture and support technical conversations that translate the strategic direction and product roadmap into feasible and defined feature requests.

If you're interested, please get in touch!
